These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, airplane, skateboard, subway, trike
5 different games are played: chess, scrabble, monopoly, bridge, backgammon
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, green, red, lilac
 1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
11. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes brown##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Transport   | airplane  | car | skateboard | subway | trike  |
| Game           | chess     | backgammon     | bridge  | scrabble   | monopoly    |
| Color         | green | red    | yellow | brown  | lilac |

