.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, may, december, february, september
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, board-games, chess, woodworking, sudoku
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, subway, boat, quad-bike
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the person driving the boat is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Birthday           | may   | december | september    | february | august |
| Hobby   | chess | woodworking     | sudoku | baking    | board-games  |
| Transport   | boat     | scooter | taxi    | quad-bike      | subway    |

