House: craftsman, futuristic, cape-cod, tower, townhouse
 1. the freelancer is on the right of the spanish##1
 2. the coach is on the right of the librarian##1
 3. the australian is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 5. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 6. the project-manager is on the far left##1
 7. the tower house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the german##1
 9. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the egyptian is the coach##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre      | zombie          | romance  | spy       | comedy     | mystery      |
| Job         | project-manager | social-worker | freelancer  | librarian   | coach    |
