 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
 9. the librarian is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the person who growsorchid is the doctor##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
