 8. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
