5 different games are played: backgammon, whist, domino, canasta, mah-jongg
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, ice-hockey, lacrosse, weightlifting
 1. the art-deco house is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Pet         | ferret  | cat  | chinchilla    | snake | hedgehog |
| House   | art-deco        | wooden  | farmhouse | tower      | victorian        |
