.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, british, russian, chinese, colombian
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, boat, helicopter, snowmobile, bike
5 different games are played: bridge, poker, go, backgammon, canasta
5 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the thai is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the chinese##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the british##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing backgammon##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Nationality      | thai      | british       | colombian         | chinese  | russian |
| Transport   | helicopter  | snowmobile | boat | taxi  | bike  |
| Game   | backgammon    | poker    | bridge        | canasta | go     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

