.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, sports, thriller, western
House: craftsman, townhouse, art-deco, modern, victorian
There 5 different types of food: banana, nectarine, avocado, artichoke, cauliflower
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, jet-ski, skateboard, motorbike
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the townhouse house##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is in the middle##1
10. the person eating banana is the victorian house##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the modern house##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | thriller | sports  | western    | adventure |
| House   | modern     | victorian     | townhouse | craftsman      | art-deco      |
| Food           | avocado       | banana     | nectarine     | cauliflower     | artichoke   |
| Transport         | helicopter | skateboard | bus  | motorbike | jet-ski   |

